        </h3>
        <p class="max-w-3xl text-base text-gray-700 md:text-lg lg:text-xl">
          We create fast, secure, and scalable websites and applications,
          combining modern technologies to deliver custom solutions tailored to
          your business needs.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="mt-4 grid divide-x divide-y divide-gray-300 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-gray-300 text-gray-800 sm:grid-cols-3 sm:divide-y-0 xl:grid-cols-3"
      >
        <div
          class="group relative bg-white transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-300/20"
        >
          <div class="relative space-y-8 p-8">
            <AddWalletIcon
              class="size-16 rounded-full border border-gray-200"
              style="color:transparent"
            />
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h4
                class="group-hover:text-primary text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 transition"
              >
                Shopify Store Design and Development
              </h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Create custom, high-converting Shopify stores with unique
                designs, seamless integrations, and optimized for e-commerce
                success.
              </p>
              <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-4">
                <li
                  class="rounded-md bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 text-sm font-semibold"
                >
                  next js
                </li>
                <li
                  class="rounded-md bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 text-sm font-semibold"
                >
                  remix js
                </li>
                <li
